Sponsored by Indeed

The world of work is evolving faster than ever before.

Indeed’s Chief Economist, Svenja Gudell, explains how AI and data are reshaping the job market, changing what employers hire for and how people work.

From tracking millions of data points to understanding shifts in skills and sectors, Indeed’s insights reveal a job market in flux. As AI disrupts industries, it’s also helping workers and companies adapt, combining human and machine strengths to create the hybrid roles of tomorrow.

Discover how Indeed is using data and AI to illuminate the future of work and empower everyone to navigate change with confidence. https://www.indeed.com/hire?kw=&sid=us_tmp_uc_always-on_sc_employerad_tn_brnd
